  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > \"Killer Apartment\" Synopsis </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Joyna, Ross, and Ivan are college classmates who agree to explore an abandoned apartment in the jungle. After entering the complex and derelict apartment, Joyna and Ivan go missing, leaving only Ross behind. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You will play as Ross, a survivor who wakes up in an abandoned apartment deep in the jungle. Your college friends Joyna and Ivan have mysteriously disappeared, and you are the only hope. In this eerie and terrifying building, you need to tread carefully, searching every corner swallowed by darkness for clues to their disappearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/2f3942ba3b8e863ab112a5f7a8b46983.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=80 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not alone. A mysterious killer lurks in the shadows of the apartment, his every breath like the whisper of death. You need to use your wits and courage, not only to solve puzzles but also to survive this cat-and-mouse game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/b10d8021d03cd7ac1b28e90e981ab3de.poster.avif?t=1742059405\" width=680 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/b10d8021d03cd7ac1b28e90e981ab3de.webm?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/b10d8021d03cd7ac1b28e90e981ab3de.mp4?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game adopts a first-person perspective, immersing you in this death-filled apartment, where every turn can bring unexpected frights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/f5d7255b4e5b11cc8325c7b95de7d628.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=80 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No one can escape this apartment; once you come, don't think about leaving. There are no easy answers, only careful observation and meticulous thinking can help you find the truth and experience the tension and excitement of a room escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/5119cd608be5169231c101ce2bdfdb40.poster.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/5119cd608be5169231c101ce2bdfdb40.webm?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/5119cd608be5169231c101ce2bdfdb40.mp4?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/3c13c620a0ac0ae0cf7e94164cef4190.poster.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/3c13c620a0ac0ae0cf7e94164cef4190.webm?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/3c13c620a0ac0ae0cf7e94164cef4190.mp4?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/b500ec9e9b25dec09f6e13235acbc1cf.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The killer can appear at any time, you need to stay vigilant, use strategies to avoid his pursuit, and feel the heart-pounding escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/6d82de82b8cf5ca22410222c17701684.poster.avif?t=1742059405\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/6d82de82b8cf5ca22410222c17701684.webm?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/6d82de82b8cf5ca22410222c17701684.mp4?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/281783ac76d095c7b70ee6c20c8a1d8e.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > As a member of the critically acclaimed \"Abnormal 1999\" series, this game will unveil the mystery of the compass and a corner of a mysterious universe based on quantum mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/071459ea4fedf49781c2ffd389ce1e18.poster.avif?t=1742059405\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/071459ea4fedf49781c2ffd389ce1e18.webm?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862730/extras/071459ea4fedf49781c2ffd389ce1e18.mp4?t=1742059405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In the 1990s, a young man established a website called Abnormal1999, which collected a large number of abnormal cases and events. At the same time, a person in charge named \"Liu Qingchun\" also established the 403 Intelligence Section, also collecting abnormal intelligence. Over the course of more than a decade, these two organizations gradually grew in size, opposing each other, and had many intelligence personnel collecting information and clues for them. The Abnormal1999 series tells these stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
